0.10.0.20 05/05/2015
Versioning update. The version number will now be in the form of a.b.c.d:
	- a, major number: this will stay 0 until something terrible happens;
	- b, minor number: this will stay 10 until I rewrite the whole thing again;
	- c, power number: this will start at 0 and will be incremented each time
	  something is added to Siχtus, like new options, new modes, new features…
	- d, issue number: this will be bumped each time I fix something

